Incompatibilities
=================

This AsciiDoc variant is incompatible with vanilla AsciiDoc in the following
ways:



1. List argument substitution
-----------------------------


=== Vanilla

In vanilla AsciiDoc any arguments enclosed in single quotes will be subject to
macro expansion,

    [quote,'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harriet_Tubman[Harriet Tubman]']

this applies to single quotes inside double quotes as well:

    [quote,"'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harriet_Tubman[Harriet Tubman]'"]


=== Variant

Arguments enclosed in single quotes will be subject to macro expansion. This
does not apply to single quotes inside double quotes.

// vim: ft=asciidoc:
